        "text_wu_intro": {
          "type": "text",
          "name": "Intro",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Most people land on HAUSTAS from one of two places: drinking unfiltered tap water, or already using a basic pitcher filter that isn't doing the whole job. Here's exactly what changes either way.</p>",
            "width": "100%",
            "max_width": "narrow",
            "alignment": "center",
            "type_preset": "rte",
            "font": "var(--font-body--family)",
            "font_size": "1.0625rem",
            "line_height": "normal",
            "letter_spacing": "normal",
            "case": "none",
            "wrap": "pretty",
            "text_color": "#5C6368",
            "background": false,
            "background_color": "#00000026",
            "corner_radius": 0,
            "padding-block-start": 10,
            "padding-block-end": 0,
            "padding-inline-start": 0,
            "padding-inline-end": 0
          },
          "blocks": {}
        },
        "custom_liquid_wu_grid": {
          "type": "custom-liquid",
          "name": "Upgrade comparison grid",
          "settings": {
            "custom_liquid": "<div id=\"hs-why-upgrade\" style=\"max-width:1040px; margin:36px auto 0; padding-inline: clamp(4px, 2vw, 16px);\">\n  <div style=\"display:grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap:40px;\">\n    <style>\n      @media screen and (min-width: 800px) {\n        #hs-why-upgrade > div { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }\n      }\n    </style>\n    <div style=\"border-top:2px solid #0F5E75; padding-top:20px;\">\n      <h3 style=\"margin:0 0 6px; font-family: var(--font-heading--family); font-weight:600; font-size:1.375rem; color:#202224;\">Upgrading From Tap Water</h3>\n      <p style=\"margin:0 0 20px; font-family: var(--font-body--family); font-size:0.9375rem; line-height:1.6; color:#5C6368;\">Municipal treatment handles the basics — it doesn't handle everything.</p>\n      <div style=\"display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:0;\">\n        <div style=\"display:flex; gap:14px; padding:14px 0; border-bottom:1px dashed #C8D1CC;\">\n          <svg width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" style=\"flex-shrink:0; margin-top:2px;\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"9\" stroke=\"#0F5E75\" stroke-width=\"1.3\"/><path d=\"M12 7v5l3 2\" stroke=\"#0F5E75\" stroke-width=\"1.3\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/></svg>\n          <div>\n            <span style=\"display:block; font-family: var(--font-heading--family); font-weight:600; font-size:0.9375rem; color:#202224; margin-bottom:3px;\">Lead &amp; Heavy Metals</span>\n            <span style=\"display:block; font-family: var(--font-body--family); font-size:0.875rem; line-height:1.6; color:#5C6368;\">The CDC states there is no known safe level of lead exposure — it can leach from aging pipes and fixtures with no taste or smell to warn you.</span>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        <div style=\"display:flex; gap:14px; padding:14px 0; border-bottom:1px dashed #C8D1CC;\">\n          <svg width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" style=\"flex-shrink:0; margin-top:2px;\"><path d=\"M12 3l6 9-6 9-6-9 6-9z\" stroke=\"#0F5E75\" stroke-width=\"1.3\"/></svg>\n          <div>\n            <span style=\"display:block; font-family: var(--font-heading--family); font-weight:600; font-size:0.9375rem; color:#202224; margin-bottom:3px;\">Chlorine &amp; Disinfection Byproducts</span>\n            <span style=\"display:block; font-family: var(--font-body--family); font-size:0.875rem; line-height:1.6; color:#5C6368;\">Necessary to keep municipal water safe from bacteria, but a well-known contributor to off tastes, odors, dry skin, and brittle hair.</span>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        <div style=\"display:flex; gap:14px; padding:14px 0; border-bottom:1px dashed #C8D1CC;\">\n          <svg width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" style=\"flex-shrink:0; margin-top:2px;\"><path d=\"M7 3h10M9 3v4a5 5 0 002 4 5 5 0 00-2 4v6M15 3v4a5 5 0 01-2 4 5 5 0 012 4v6M7 21h10\" stroke=\"#0F5E75\" stroke-width=\"1.3\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/></svg>\n          <div>\n            <span style=\"display:block; font-family: var(--font-heading--family); font-weight:600; font-size:0.9375rem; color:#202224; margin-bottom:3px;\">PFAS (\"Forever Chemicals\")</span>\n            <span style=\"display:block; font-family: var(--font-body--family); font-size:0.875rem; line-height:1.6; color:#5C6368;\">Synthetic chemicals that don't break down in the environment or the body. The EPA links long-term exposure to increased health risks.</span>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        <div style=\"display:flex; gap:14px; padding:14px 0;\">\n          <svg width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" style=\"flex-shrink:0; margin-top:2px;\"><circle cx=\"7\" cy=\"8\" r=\"1.4\" fill=\"#0F5E75\"/><circle cx=\"13\" cy=\"6\" r=\"1\" fill=\"#0F5E75\"/><circle cx=\"17\" cy=\"11\" r=\"1.4\" fill=\"#0F5E75\"/><circle cx=\"9\" cy=\"15\" r=\"1\" fill=\"#0F5E75\"/><circle cx=\"15\" cy=\"17\" r=\"1.4\" fill=\"#0F5E75\"/></svg>\n          <div>\n            <span style=\"display:block; font-family: var(--font-heading--family); font-weight:600; font-size:0.9375rem; color:#202224; margin-bottom:3px;\">Microplastics &amp; Sediment</span>\n            <span style=\"display:block; font-family: var(--font-body--family); font-size:0.875rem; line-height:1.6; color:#5C6368;\">Researchers have detected microplastic particles in tap water samples worldwide — sediment filtration is one of the simplest ways to reduce daily exposure.</span>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"border-top:2px solid #C9A24B; padding-top:20px;\">\n      <h3 style=\"margin:0 0 6px; font-family: var(--font-heading--family); font-weight:600; font-size:1.375rem; color:#202224;\">Upgrading From A Pitcher Filter</h3>\n      <p style=\"margin:0 0 20px; font-family: var(--font-body--family); font-size:0.9375rem; line-height:1.6; color:#5C6368;\">A basic carbon filter is better than nothing — it's just not built for the whole job.</p>\n      <div style=\"display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:0;\">\n        <div style=\"display:flex; gap:14px; padding:14px 0; border-bottom:1px dashed #C8D1CC;\">\n          <svg width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" style=\"flex-shrink:0; margin-top:2px;\"><rect x=\"7\" y=\"4\" width=\"10\" height=\"16\" rx=\"1\" stroke=\"#C9A24B\" stroke-width=\"1.3\"/><line x1=\"7\" y1=\"10\" x2=\"17\" y2=\"10\" stroke=\"#C9A24B\" stroke-width=\"1\"/></svg>\n          <div>\n            <span style=\"display:block; font-family: var(--font-heading--family); font-weight:600; font-size:0.9375rem; color:#202224; margin-bottom:3px;\">Only 1-Stage Carbon Filtration</span>\n            <span style=\"display:block; font-family: var(--font-body--family); font-size:0.875rem; line-height:1.6; color:#5C6368;\">Improves taste and odor, but doesn't address heavy metals or fine sediment the way a multi-stage system does.</span>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        <div style=\"display:flex; gap:14px; padding:14px 0; border-bottom:1px dashed #C8D1CC;\">\n          <svg width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" style=\"flex-shrink:0; margin-top:2px;\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"9\" stroke=\"#C9A24B\" stroke-width=\"1.3\"/><path d=\"M12 8v4l2.5 1.5\" stroke=\"#C9A24B\" stroke-width=\"1.3\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/></svg>\n          <div>\n            <span style=\"display:block; font-family: var(--font-heading--family); font-weight:600; font-size:0.9375rem; color:#202224; margin-bottom:3px;\">~2-Month Cartridge Life</span>\n            <span style=\"display:block; font-family: var(--font-body--family); font-size:0.875rem; line-height:1.6; color:#5C6368;\">Needs replacing roughly every 2 months versus HAUSTAS's 6-month service life — easy to forget, easy to run past its effective window.</span>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        <div style=\"display:flex; gap:14px; padding:14px 0; border-bottom:1px dashed #C8D1CC;\">\n          <svg width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" style=\"flex-shrink:0; margin-top:2px;\"><path d=\"M12 3l2.5 5.5L20 9l-4 4 1 6-5-3-5 3 1-6-4-4 5.5-.5z\" stroke=\"#C9A24B\" stroke-width=\"1.1\"/></svg>\n          <div>\n            <span style=\"display:block; font-family: var(--font-heading--family); font-weight:600; font-size:0.9375rem; color:#202224; margin-bottom:3px;\">No Independent Certification</span>\n            <span style=\"display:block; font-family: var(--font-body--family); font-size:0.875rem; line-height:1.6; color:#5C6368;\">Most basic pitcher filters carry no NSF/ANSI certification — you're taking the manufacturer's word for what it actually removes.</span>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        <div style=\"display:flex; gap:14px; padding:14px 0;\">\n          <svg width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" style=\"flex-shrink:0; margin-top:2px;\"><path d=\"M4 12h16M15 6l5 6-5 6\" stroke=\"#C9A24B\" stroke-width=\"1.3\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/></svg>\n          <div>\n            <span style=\"display:block; font-family: var(--font-heading--family); font-weight:600; font-size:0.9375rem; color:#202224; margin-bottom:3px;\">No Warranty, No Trial</span>\n            <span style=\"display:block; font-family: var(--font-body--family); font-size:0.875rem; line-height:1.6; color:#5C6368;\">If it doesn't work for your water or your routine, there's no 100-night trial and no 15-year warranty to fall back on.</span>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n"
          },
          "blocks": {}
        },
